	<div data-zesty-id="content:block:6-bcfbdaa6d3-vjj3qs:27:90:0:19">{{block('/-/block/hero_full.html?variant=7-84f6d3c1e5-nqxvsv')}}</div>
	<div class="p-6 rounded-5 bg-light mb-18" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:16:91">
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:16:91-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<h6 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:88">Volunteer with The Salvation Army<br>
Of Greater Charlotte</h6>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:9">
	Choose from serving meals at the Center of Hope, organizing collection drives for homeless families, or helping to empower youth through our Salvation Army Youth Programs.&nbsp;Your contribution can profoundly impact lives. Why not start today?
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:3:38"><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/a5b73512-5fdb-42af-9f17-1a71c5db544a_NEW+Volunteer+Application+Packet+9-25.pdf" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Volunteer Application</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:4:43"></div>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:5:55"><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:6:44"><strong><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/5f602b3d-cffc-4c64-aac2-22a9340a3f1c_Background+Check+Documents.pdf">Background Check Documents</a></strong></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:7:99"></div>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:8:60">
	Please only complete the background check and volunteer application if you are planning on volunteering with our Salvation Army Youth Programs&nbsp;or the Center of Hope Shelter for Women and Children. <strong>You do not have to fill them out if you are volunteering at our Christmas Center.</strong>
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:10:25"></div>
<div class="row g-3 my-3 align-items-stretch" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:13:39">
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 d-flex flex-column" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:13:39-1:2 Columns - Equal:0">
<div class="card-wysiwyg-body d-flex flex-column h-100 w-100 flex-fill rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-area text-dark" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:9:27"><p>
	<iframe frameborder="0" height="1000" id="myFrame" name="myFrame" src="https://www.cervistech.com/acts/webreg/eventwebreglist.php?org_id=0160" title="CERVIS Opportunity Registration" width="750"></iframe>
</p></div>
				</div>
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 d-flex flex-column" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:13:39-1:2 Columns - Equal:1">
<div class="card-wysiwyg-body d-flex flex-column h-100 w-100 flex-fill rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-area text-dark" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:11:56"><p>
	<img class="img-fluid rounded d-block mx-auto" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/cec926a0-9da5-4ba6-87c3-be6204abbe7c_Meal+Service+Volunteer.png" style="display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
</p>

<p>
	<strong>Please click the links below to view ways to engage and give back.</strong>
</p>

<p>
	The Salvation Army is unable to accommodate court ordered and lawyer suggested community service requests.
</p>

<p>
	<strong><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/29e85ce4-6a51-44a7-8c18-d752056d7643_Center+of+Hope+Meal+Service.pdf">Center of Hope Meal Service</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Providing nourishment and comfort to individuals and families experiencing homelessness.
</p>

<p>
	<strong><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/1702429a-e3a3-45a9-86dd-b69014149772_Group+Adopt+a+Meal+Overview.pdf">Adopt a Meal Program</a>: </strong> This program provides a much-needed meal to the women and children at our Center of Hope Homeless Shelter. Organizations, church groups, corporate teams, and individuals are needed to provide meals for the families staying with us.&nbsp;
</p>

<p>
	<strong><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/c3583a11-357c-412c-bf39-0a9115f79577_Group+Engagement+Packet+2025.pdf">Group Opportunities</a>:</strong>&nbsp;We can accommodate your group’s desire to do something good together – whether family, friends, coworkers, civic or church groups.&nbsp;
</p>

<p>
	<em><strong>Other Group and&nbsp;Individual Volunteer Opportunities:</strong></em>
</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/967d0613-4c56-4c75-91dd-34ad47624d00_Donation+Information.pdf">Acceptable Donations for the Center of Hope</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/82d5cfa3-5613-415a-9d88-c450f2e1db7d_Welcome+Home+Basket+Project+2025.pdf">Welcome Home Baskets</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/338c8689-3ad9-4ba4-94ff-b0fc28b471a9_Dignity+Drive+Flyer+2025.pdf">Dignity Drive for new underwear</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/821a35f8-2e25-41bb-99cf-7fa25fc66866_Hope+Bundles.pdf">Hope Bundles</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/ff0cd328-1459-44a9-b5d7-ea2467dde00a_Linen+and+Bedding+Drive.pdf">Linen and Bedding Drive</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/e61f67b0-8b8c-498d-a8e7-eabd85f52ac9_Snack+Pack+Program+Overview+NEW+4226.pdf">Snack Pack Program</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/19be9fd7-6c43-4c7b-b9bb-e9c01f04ecc1_Teen+Project+Instructions.pdf">Teen Project Instructions</a></li>
</ul></div>
